					<description><![CDATA[We have been slow with posting/publishing some annual database files from AFU.&#160;AFU is overwhelmed with incoming materials. This naturally puts our immediate priorities on trying to accomplish the very first sort-out of hundreds of boxes of materials into our archival system.&#160; In February we finished the 2020 alphabetic catalogue of all magazines, newsletters and other [&#8230;]]]></description>
		
		
		
			</item>
		<item>
		<title>Nils-Olof Jacobson’s archive to AFU</title>
		<link>https://www.afu.se/afu2/?p=8590</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Clas Svahn]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2020 14:43:59 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[New donations]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.afu.se/afu2/?p=8590</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[On June 10–11th AFU:s board member Carl-Anton Mattsson travelled with me (Clas Svahn) to Kristianstad and Färjestaden to bring two donations to AFU. One small, 50 books, from the estate of UFO-Aktuellt subscriber Ingemar Karlsson who had passed away, and one large from the late psychiatrist and author Nils-Olof Jacobson (1937–2017). Jacobson had a life [&#8230;]]]></description>
		
		
		
			</item>
		<item>
