		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Clas Svahn]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2020 10:40:24 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[New acquisitions]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[News]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.afu.se/afu2/?p=8571</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[In the middle of January Ukraine ufologist Igor Kalytyuk and his team at Global Archive for the second time donated a copy of its ever expanding extensive digital archive in the form of a series of blue-ray discs to AFU. The Ukraine based center started in January 2011 and is headed by Igor Kalytyuk (picture [&#8230;]]]></description>
		
		
		
			</item>
