					<description><![CDATA[On Saturday 7 December AFU held its annual meeting at the AFU HQ in Norrköping. At the meeting the board discussed plans to find another location for all of the three kilometers of shelf space that are now in 14 different localities in the same area in Norrköping and instead to make a move to [&#8230;]]]></description>
		
		
		
